Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked to Fujimiya-san for the first time.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Good for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wish finally came true.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.60,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been saying how you wanted to talk to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But she turned me down.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.06,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked her to be my friend, but she turned me down.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually asked her?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was happy I asked, but that she couldn't.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What could she have meant, Shougo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cold, Shougo!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're a pain.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.08,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she just turning you down politely?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.26,0:04:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so too, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.93,0:04:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If it bothers you so much, \Nwhy don't you go ask her?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.28,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw her heading for the roof.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.56,0:04:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.48,0:04:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the roof always locked?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hase-kun?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}this{\i0} is where you eat lunch every day.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Whoa! The view is great up here!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.51,0:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been to the roof before, so I had no idea.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great having the place to yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like your own box seat.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san, are you...{oh shit, it's keyaids}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a cold? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were coughing earlier too.
