Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fujimiya-san...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.53,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the class rep for math, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.31,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to turn in my notes yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.48,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could convince the teacher to take these?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san sure is cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's her problem?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's chilly today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it just me?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I eat here, too?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.65,0:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend already finished his, and now he's napping.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why what?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifth period's P.E., right?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the energy for P.E. in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hase-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.90,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone say you couldn't?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.74,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are your parents so strict
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.29,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that they say you have to spend all your time studying instead?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nobody told me I couldn't.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All the same...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.76,0:07:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{second demo}There's no way I can do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.46,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you were coughing on purpose, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you keep up the act?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Because...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.38,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you thank me back then?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san, you're the math—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.43,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the math class rep because you're good at math, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to carry those?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Hase-kun...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.88,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.36,0:08:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For helping me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bye!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd kept acting cold toward me,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have asked you \Nto be friends like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.22,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to avoid talking to you, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.22,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to at least thank you \Nafter you helped me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.55,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} a good person!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to be friends,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but let's have lunch again tomorrow.{oh god hnnng}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.75,0:09:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.62,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just eat lunch together.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as friends or anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.71,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... See you here on the roof tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't talk to me in class.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.32,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd turned me down again, \NI don't know what I would've done.
