Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat{ together}!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating together really does make food taste better.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.16,0:10:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's play cards{ next}!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cards?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.66,0:10:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone plays cards at lunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.20,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We usually play President...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you need more than two players for that.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Old Maid?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess we can't play that, either.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try Concentration, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.88,0:11:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So the last card is...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,this one?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost five times in a row.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.98,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an incredible memory, Fujimiya-san.{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.50,0:11:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're great at math, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.86,0:11:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not {\i1}great{\i0} at it, but I've always enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.29,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Man. I couldn't do math to save my life.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I really admire you.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.26,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything to do at home, \Nso all I do is study.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.03,0:11:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I have nothing to do, I go out.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hm?}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.36,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hase-kun, when you go out with your friends, where do you go?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Karaoke, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is karaoke fun?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you've never tried karaoke?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.29,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come with me sometime?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's out of the question!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault for asking out of the blue.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you get a chance to someday.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.92,0:12:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All finished!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm still hungry.
