Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.32,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have bought some dessert.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.82,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure this would fill you up either, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a new crêpe place near the station!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Crêpes, huh? Sounds good.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like crêpes, too?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.33,0:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I like them with chocolate custard.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite filling is strawberries and whipped cream.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but blueberry cheesecake is good, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place I go with my mom all the time.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They only have one bench, \Nso people are always fighting over it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how this place will be.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully they'll have lots of seating.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.30,0:13:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, just in case you wanted to go with anyone!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.80,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't saying {\i1}we{\i0} should go together!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind if—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not like we're friends!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're still not friends, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san, what do you think friends are?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.17,0:13:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.08,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, what do you think they talk about?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Love?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.55,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no one I like right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were interested in anyone, it'd probably be...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.42,0:14:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not friends, though, \Nso we can't talk about love.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.96,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wash this later, so just leave it here.
