Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All finished!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lunch was good, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.05,0:15:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Fujimiya-san, you hardly ate anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that hungry today.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.59,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Next period is biology, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.07,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I hope I don't doze off. What'll I do if I fail?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.20,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's math that I'm almost failing.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san, you're good at math, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Why don't we—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hase-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.87,0:15:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why not?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you suddenly—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.30,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you from the start: I can't make friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.39,0:16:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd like you to forget any of this ever happened.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.67,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll forget everything, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.26,0:16:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.01,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just forget.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you can't either, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} forget!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Every Monday,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.32,0:16:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,all my good memories disappear.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.72,0:16:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just my good memories, either.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.09,0:16:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All my memories of people I'm close to \Nor want to spend more time with
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.38,0:16:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,are completely reset every week.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The only exception is my family.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.86,0:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't have any memories of my friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.91,0:17:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.07,0:17:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not friends yet, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then—
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.26,0:17:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this much I'm certain of.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.62,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories of you will all disappear.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.61,0:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that.
