Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.86,0:17:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When was the last time we did this?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.17,0:17:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san told me not to talk to her anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.96,0:17:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she'd forget me, \Nand that I should forget her too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.55,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That must mean...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She really hates you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.19,0:18:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya's always cut herself off \Nfrom the rest of the class.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can never tell what she's thinking.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you like about her?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.61,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Her face.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so simple.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares why I like her?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.90,0:18:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only become friends by talking to people and finding out whether you get along.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.03,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't something you can consciously work toward.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you want to date her, that's a different story.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.89,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san isn't as cold as everyone thinks.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cheerful and talkative.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said we should eat lunch together,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,she even waited for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If people just talked to her,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.48,0:18:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd realize she's a nice girl that anyone'd want to be friends with.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.23,0:19:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's kind, honest, and a good person.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about sappy.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.31,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you cringing at?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.58,0:19:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if she really is like that,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.15,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're the only one who's seen it, it must mean you're special to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.21,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come a long way from the things \Nyou were stressing out about on Monday.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shougo...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.75,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've come this far, you might as well go for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.46,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaori? Your father bought a cake.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll have some later.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.57,0:20:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,740)}We're not friends...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.80,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.98,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that moment, I finally understood Fujimiya-san's words.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.89,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She wasn't lying when she said she'd lose her memories.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her memories of the week she'd spent with me were completely gone.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every Monday,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.11,0:21:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the fun times and moments of understanding she's had with others are reset,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she starts over from the beginning.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't want to go through that.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.50,0:21:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That must be why she never tries to make any friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...{"Uh..."?}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.19,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't need anything, then...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimiya-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I know the truth.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fujimiya-san actually...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.89,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wants friends more than anyone!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.61,0:21:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I came to a decision, there and then.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd say it as often as I had to.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.70,0:21:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like for us to be friends.
